description: A joke about starting a diet but having too much to handle.
title: Too Much on Plate
n_1: Tom and Sara were having lunch together.
c1_1: I'd like to start a diet,
n_2: Tom looked at his plate piled high with food.
c1_2: But I've got too much on my plate right now.
c2_3: Sure, if you can finish that!
n_4: They both enjoyed their meal, still chuckling.
